nars.nar

Class AbstractNAR

  • java.lang.Object
    • nars.NAR
      • nars.nar.AbstractNAR
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, Level
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractAlann, Default, Terminal

    public abstract class AbstractNAR
extends NAR
    Default set of NAR parameters which have been classically used for development.

    WARNING this Seed is not immutable yet because it extends Param, which is supposed to be per-instance/mutable. So do not attempt to create multiple NAR with the same Default seed model
